  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And over on the other side near the-- of the yard, near the entrance to the building, I saw one young woman standing, and I decided to approach her.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went up to her and asked her about her companions and how they all were, and we exchanged some words in German.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I asked her, you know, whether-- where they had been.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she told me that they had been on a death march since-- more-- with some stops since January of that year.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I asked her to take me inside and let me see the others.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we went inside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, it's nearly impossible to describe the scene that I found inside, with all these women scattered on the floor in-- in various stages of illness, and some of them obviously quite close to death, and in rags and without blankets or-- quite obviously without food.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it-- it was something that one never, never can forget.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And even I, who had steeled myself, knowing-- having known by that time the extent of the-- of the German Nazi mentality, knew that I should steel myself against anything we might find.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But even that was simply too overwhelming.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
